name: Catgirl Optimus
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
What is $OPTIG?
Catgirl Optimus is a community-driven project, made to pay homage to Elon Musk's vision of a Catgirl Optimus Robot, through the blockchain. 

How many $OPTIG coins are there in circulation? 
Catgirl Optimus launched with an initial, fixed circulating supply of 1,000,000,000 tokens. This number is deflationary, as $OPTIG contract contains an automatic token burn feature.

$OPTIG vision:
Catgirl Optimus aims to create brand awareness and perpetuate the narrative of the Catgirl Optimus AI bot; eventually becoming a top cryptocurrency and being recognized as such. By utilizing means of organic growth, marketing, and social media exposure, $OPTIG aims to be recognized by and provide Elon Musk with ideas for the Catgirl version of Optimus AI bot.
